dc_description_s: This data layer represents zoning for Washington County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase NWashington_Zoning_2018.gdbN. The feature layers included in this geodatabase are NWashington_Floodplain_2018N and NWashington_Shoreland_2018N.
dct_provenance_s: Arthur H. Robinson Map Library - University of Wisconsin
dc_creator_sm: Washington County Geographic Information System Division
dc_subject_sm: Zoning - Maps, City Planning, County Ordinances
